      WHHHOOOOOOWWWWW!!!!!!

0   - Decreases the number of gun mountings.

1-4 - Selects the next smaller gun on the front, the back,
      the top or the bottom turret.

C   - Decreases the number of cabins

Y   - Decreases the cargo space
